## run

- `$ conda activate utp `
- `$ conda run -n utp python utp.py`
- `$ pip install pyyaml click`

## install locally

- `$ pip install --editable .`

## upload

requirements

- `$ pip install twine`
- `$ chmod + ./upload.sh`

upload

- `$ ./upload.sh`
